question: amusement park date? what?
answer: As Yun Casting let slip (and as @mackmeta and @tjkiahgb pointed out) the Andi Mack cast will be filming in Farmington, Utah on Thursday of this week and will require extras that are able to ride rides all day. The location they’re filming in has an amusement park. Since Luke is back in SLC and they’re filming that episode this week, it can be concluded that Luke will be filming that day with Josh since his storyline mainly features Cyrus.

summary: If you’re like me, you watch a lot shows (I’m watching like 15+ right now) and it’s hard to remember them all. Andi Mack is...
body:
If you’re like me, you watch a lot shows (I’m watching like 15+ right now) and it’s hard to remember them all. Andi Mack is coming back soon so I want to introduce you all to the lifesaver that is TV Time.

It helps me keep track of all my shows (running AND off-air!) while having a fun social media design to the app. It even tells you how many hours you’ve spent watching TV and how many episodes left you have with all your shows combined. There’s literally so much great things about the app that I can’t put them all in one post. It’s a TV lovers dream! And I’m not even sponsored. I just really like this app and feel like a lot of people could benefit from it. It’s also the fall season so everything is coming back (The Flash, Riverdale, Daredevil.) so we all need to prepare.
